subject: College Athletics
Basketball
NCAA Basketball Tournament
lead_paragraph: Epiphanny Prince scored 23 points and Kia Vaughn added a season-high 13 on Friday to help No. 14 Rutgers win its fifth consecutive game, 61-29, over Lafayette.
